<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٨٠ - وَحَدَّثَنَاهُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5983">‌مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ يَحْيَى </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5923">‌أَبُو غَسَّانَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/611">‌إِسْرَائِيلُ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ فِيهِ:</span> <span class="c2">«وَغَسَلَ ذِرَاعَيْهِ ثَلَاثًا»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>